        "text": " and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "πεισμονή",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". He gives the latter word a transitive meaning, Studium persuadendi aliis ea quæ nobis placent et probantur—",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The desire to persuade others of what pleases ourselves and meets our approval",
        "children": []
      },
      {
